column2: Ma' wáaj ta bine'ex merkaado táan a báaxale'ex báaxal tu naajil báaxal

column1: Tene' ts'oka'an wáaj in beel yaan wáaj in bin koonol merkaado
column2: Leti'obe' ts'oka'an wáaj u beelo'ob yaan wáaj u bino'ob koonol merkaado

column1: Táan wáaj a xook tu naajil xook sáansamal kin bin koonol merkaado
column2: Táan wáaj a xooke'ex xook tu naajil xook sáansamal ka bine'ex koonol merkaado

column1: Jbinen yéetel in éetailo'ob merkaado yaan in boon tu naajil xook
column2: Jbinech yéetel a éetailo'ob merkaado yaan a boon tu naajil xook

column1: Ma' in wojel u ja'abili' ts'oka'an wáaj in beel
column2: Ma' u yojelo'ob u ja'abili' ts'oka'an wáaj a beele'ex

column1: Táan in meyaj ich kool ba'atelnajen te' tu kúuchil báaxalo'
column2: Táan u meyajo'ob ich kool ba'atelnajo'ob te' tu kúuchil báaxalo'

column1: Yaan in báaxal tu naajil báaxal yaan in xook tu naajil xook
column2: Yaan k báaxal tu naajil báaxal yaan k xook tu naajil xook

column1: Yaan wáaj a xook tu naajil xook ma' tin wu'uyik ooxoli'
column2: Yaan wáaj u xooko'ob tu naajil xook ma' tu yu'ubiko'ob ooxoli'

column1: Táan in bin koonol merkaado jweenen ich kool
column2: Táan a bin koonol merkaado jweenech ich kool

column1: Teche' áak'ab wáaj ka bin merkaado jach wáaj k'a'abéet a bin k'íiwikil koonol
column2: Leti'e' áak'ab wáaj ku bin merkaado jach k'a'abéet wáaj u bin tu k'íiwikil koonol

column1: Tene' ts'oka'an wáaj in beel ma' tin wilaj u sáastal tin kaajali'
column2: To'one' ts'oka'an wáaj k beel ma' tak ilaj u sáastal k kaajali'

column1: Yaan in xook tu naajil xook ma' in wojel u ja'abili'
column2: Yaan u xook tu naajil xook ma' u yojel u ja'abili'

column1: Ma' wáaj jach k'a'abéet in bin merkaadoi' ma' táan in bin koonol tu k'íiwikil koonol
column2: Ma' wáaj jach k'a'abéet u bino'ob merkaadoi' ma' táan u bino'ob koonol tu k'íiwikil koonol

column1: Tene' ti' in taali' óok'otnajen tu naajil xook
column2: To'one' ti' in taalo'oni' óok'otnajo'on tu naajil xook

column1: Yaan wáaj a xook tu naajil xook ki'imak in wóol in bin merkaado
column2: Yaan wáaj u xooko'ob tu naajil xook ki'imak u yóolo'ob u bino'ob merkaado

column1: Ta'aytak in chukik u ja'abil yaan wáaj a báaxal tu naajil báaxal
column2: Ta'aytak u chukiko'ob u ja'abil yaan wáaj u báaxalo'ob tu naajil báaxal

column1: Tin míistik in najil tene' kin bin paak'áal ich kool
column2: Táan a míistik in najil teche' ka bin paak'áal ich kool

column1: Ook'in in bin tu k'íiwikil koonol táan wáaj a boon tu naajil xook
column2: Ook'in a bine'ex k'íiwikil koonol táan wáaj a boone'ex xook tu naajil xook

column1: Táan wáaj a báaxal tu naajil báaxal ts'oka'an wáaj in beel
column2: Táan wáaj k báaxal tu naajil báaxal ts'oka'an wáaj k beel

column1: Táan in meyaj ich kool k'aaynajen tu naajil xook
column2: Táan a meyaje'ex ich kool k'aaynaje'ex tu naajil xook

column1: Ma' ts'oka'an in beeli' tene' áak'ab kin bin tu k'íiwikil koonol
column2: Ma' ts'oka'an k beeli' to'one' áak'ab k bin tu k'íiwikil koonol

column1: Jbinen áalkab te' taam paarkéeo' tene' ajkoonolen ichil merkaado
column2: To'one' bino'on áalkab te' taam paarkéeo' to'one' ajkoonolo'on ichil merkaado

column1: Tan in k'íilkab ma' jach k'a'abéet in bin tu k'íiwikil koonoli'
column2: Tan a k'íilkabe'ex ma' jach k'a'abéet a bine'ex k'íiwikil koonoli'

column1: Ma' ts'oka'an in beeli' yaan wáaj in bin ich kool
column2: Ma' ts'oka'an k beeli' yaan wáaj ek bin ich kool
